都係可以執架啫。<br />\n<br />\n文化上，日本同韓國都大男人架喇，你要人地尊重女性一定好難，雖然香港同歐美比都唔算男女平等，但日韓一定更加差；不過我又唔係絲，關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW見到有人話「日本仔又瘦又弱」<br />\n咩地方都有健身友同頹友架喇，你可唔可以唔好咁on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c087fd2d41e4dd0f59cc89d92daee1f8963e050","tid":974891,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36f1304332846d9dac10c031236ab19a18a40fdf","tid":974891,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c087fd2d41e4dd0f59cc89d92daee1f8963e050","tid":974891,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"韓國人碌九全球最細，0仔會中意？"},{"pid":"c5e51bc6d0a76fe27d3c0c72efb9f6df5d02dabc","tid":974891,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55323f63d27d3a27011cdd166678a0acf50c66e","tid":974891,"uid":169980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"0仔都唔揀韓仔la，咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1同0都揀架仔la<br />\n利申: 10仔，都係有固定男朋友"},{"pid":"27b3f865de2fd8e0d1d0b8732e6969968cf5d3db","tid":974891,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"韓國一線偶像<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojs4QuB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fojs4QuB.png&h=8afbfe87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本一線偶像<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qf6xeWp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqf6xeWp.png&h=c30db93f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e75b5ea2947a777585bb11604e6abfe13b217d4a","tid":974891,"uid":221265,"like":0